List all web forums about Emacs all over the world.  See also EmacsNewsgroups, EmacsMailingLists and EmacsPages for alternatives.

* [http://emacs.stackexchange.com Emacs StackExchange] -- you can ask technical questions there
* [http://www.reddit.com/r/emacs reddit.com/r/emacs] -- great for general discussions and interesting links
* https://www.quora.com/topic/Emacs -- opinions, some technical discussions
* Chinese -- [http://forum.emacs-china.org/ forum.emacs-china.org]




